{"tid":2114966,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥德羅施匡翹確診武肺  傳播鏈涉逾百人 娛圈爆疫","createTime":"2020-07-19T07:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T00:31:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f320797e6dba0dfe09f0ce9cc00c675521ceece8","tid":2114966,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200719/QXECEYLZQAPMZIAAZ6K26CFKNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200719%2FQXECEYLZQAPMZIAAZ6K26CFKNQ%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB9E6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=e8df3257\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200719%2FQXECEYLZQAPMZIAAZ6K26CFKNQ%2F&h=120f3922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200719/QXECEYLZQAPMZIAAZ6K26CFKNQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n麥德羅施匡翹確診武肺 <br />\n傳播鏈涉逾百人 娛圈爆疫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎在香港再度爆發，現年24歲的女歌手施匡翹、其經理人劉麗萍（Apple姐）及宣傳人員阿佳確診不幸中招，Apple姐男友、歌手麥德羅亦已確診，四人現於隔離病房治療。由於施匡翹及阿佳近日曾踏足多個電台、電視台，接觸過百人，令娛圈人心惶惶，雷深如、薛凱琪等也成為高危人士。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蔣嘉瑩發燒 薛凱琪急檢查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5wpd7aQA31vIVostvsEKfp5VTi0=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/47OHDFV4UF245PXSG64V2R4TRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5wpd7aQA31vIVostvsEKfp5VTi0%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F47OHDFV4UF245PXSG64V2R4TRI.jpg&h=e0080af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施匡翹及Apple姐在本月8日曾出席慈善音樂會，當時全部人均沒有戴上口罩，同場的J.Arie、蔣嘉瑩及謝高晉成為高危人士。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AG6yS4_dedLktzFM9el_1IheBQI=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LNYOTG5IZBLKH7VBAZFUDX3COU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAG6yS4_dedLktzFM9el_1IheBQI%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLNYOTG5IZBLKH7VBAZFUDX3COU.jpg&h=b58db920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple姐現於伊利沙伯醫院留醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-aWS2E7-t4j4CuNtwIxReQ31NjU=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KP5JQFMA2MVTT57RNYZJXHSN64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-aWS2E7-t4j4CuNtwIxReQ31NjU%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKP5JQFMA2MVTT57RNYZJXHSN64.jpg&h=06ef34ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有指麥德羅（右）8日前曾與謝天華（左）等在尖沙咀飯敍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ytpDmHKi9yulUF3MCOby0jOSJoA=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZZ3ARZCDBT4HB5RTA7CHANV62Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FytpDmHKi9yulUF3MCOby0jOSJoA%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZZ3ARZCDBT4HB5RTA7CHANV62Y.jpg&h=678edf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥德羅昨日凌晨確診，現於威院留醫。<br />\n<br />\n現年61歲的麥德羅昨日凌晨確診武漢肺炎，被衞生防護中心傳染病處列為個案編號1739的尖沙嘴歌手。麥德羅昨日接受《蘋果》訪問，他指近一、兩日開始有武肺病徵：「𠵱家有啲頭㷫、喉嚨痛、肚瀉，呢一兩日發燒，所以睇醫生。」他於昨日凌晨入院，經病毒檢測後證實初步確診，不過他就表示近日沒有相約圈中人見面，只是見女朋友Apple姐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XVvJV4d2n3yTCXK4yu5KQ2FJjD0=/1106x851/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N5YY4VFWOPZVF7O2TILXHHFQNA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXVvJV4d2n3yTCXK4yu5KQ2FJjD0%3D%2F1106x851%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN5YY4VFWOPZVF7O2TILXHHFQNA.gif&h=3282803f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌迷聚會後胃痛<br />\n<br />\n麥德羅透露本月10日曾在尖沙嘴麼地道一間私人場所舉行約40人的歌迷聚會︰「參加完聚會後，噚日起身覺得唔舒服。所以去睇醫生，醫生叫我驗口水，話我似，醫生檢查完。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n麥德羅發現自己「中招」後，女友劉麗萍也立刻做檢測，同樣確診，現於伊利沙伯醫院留醫。Apple姐旗下歌手施匡翹也受感染，《蘋果》昨日致電施匡翹，她禮貌地直認：「我𠵱家喺醫院，啱啱做咗檢測呈陽性，𠵱家等緊醫生安排，唔。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n施匡翹（左）7月8日出席活動與蔣嘉瑩及謝高晉攬頭攬頸，或有機會播毒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C86sizCvQszcAB47stUE6Rj3RLM=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHQOZ74O5HWBGMDAQAY6ADVRQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC86sizCvQszcAB47stUE6Rj3RLM%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHQOZ74O5HWBGMDAQAY6ADVRQE.jpg&h=b2adafb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施匡翹（左二）每周到新城主持節目，其他主持謝高晉、吳燚曦及林子謙成為高危人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電台電視台中招<br />\n<br />\n施匡翹的宣傳人員阿佳昨日也確診武肺，由於阿佳早前曾為不少藝人，包括何雁詩、蘇慧恩、施匡翹、泫希及雷深如等做宣傳，曾踏足新城、商台、港台、無綫及香港開電視，牽涉人士逾百人。據悉，施匡翹與阿佳連日來。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n阿佳大前日曾到無綫參加《勁歌金曲》錄影，當時阿佳曾與工作人員交談，當晚出席的歌手有蔣嘉瑩、J.Arie、溫碧霞及Dear Jane等，翌日晚上阿佳又跟《勁歌》工作人員。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ztxc-cXlb1Onnz6xKJlsJPVQl_I=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OCIHDQ5MSCHWWPLWHTF6ZNKZL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZtxc-cXlb1Onnz6xKJlsJPVQl_I%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOCIHDQ5MSCHWWPLWHTF6ZNKZL4.jpg&h=a785d464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宣傳阿佳近日曾到佐敦一間茶餐廳用餐。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\nApple公司發言人昨晚回覆《蘋果》：「Apple姐、麥德羅、施匡翹都中咗招，基於有工作接觸，謝高晉同蔣嘉瑩喺醫院等緊。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n施匡翹去年加入加臻世娛樂有限公司，成為Apple姐旗下藝人，並與師姐蔣嘉瑩翻唱劇集《我和殭屍有個約會》的主題曲《假如真的再有約會》，又推出首支個人單曲《初心》。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ac5ec00b0deaffb11c210fbe0c9342340c89c8bb","tid":2114966,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8de7d64ff442dcf1f5b4cabe63f74b29b4435e","tid":2114966,"uid":105232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"442ac78b81dccff1a884a015c01d956735466da7","tid":2114966,"uid":9747,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"全部都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到第一眼以為麥德羅施匡翹係鬼佬譯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb83ccf4d79179a8d4fb50fbfdd43c949697289c","tid":2114966,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:00:34.000Z","msg":"Who <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324a568ca6e2d261f205ff51278745fc4a86f9a7","tid":2114966,"uid":103050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"成班都唔知乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如淨係講有藝人確診算鳩數"},{"pid":"6d54cff3aed283a361e23f2bf0d2d88dc9400246","tid":2114966,"uid":354461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"冇個識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9f74295fff532abd545a14cd1498e4cd9b0f28","tid":2114966,"uid":38218,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"442ac78b81dccff1a884a015c01d956735466da7","tid":2114966,"uid":9747,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"全部都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到第一眼以為麥德羅施匡翹係鬼佬譯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:23:09.000Z",